<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="run-take-the-risk-of-doing-sth">run / take the risk of doing sth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>冒险做某事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mary couldn’t take the risk of leaving her baby alone even for a short time. 
玛丽不敢冒险让她的孩子独自待着，即使是很短的时间。</p></div></div>